responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "54503A5546F7295AAED5BA908545DB68", "More than trophy of power, yes. The Horn, it is tied to my authority, my role as leader, my vision for our people. If it is lost, or taken... it casts doubt on my leadership.
